name: TREKTRENDY DOES DUBAI SHEIKH SYLE!  - #SE of 12
description: Along my journey to do 12 countries in 12 months, I spend a long weekend in Dubai. Seeing as I'd already visited the UAE in February 2015, I thought i'd put together this special edition of TrekTrendy TV. Watch where I climb to the 124th floor of the Burj Khalifa, explore the Dubai mall, sail along the venetian canals of the Madinat and have a selfie in a traditional arabic Thawb!
